TinyFugue on Windows
====================

The supported Windows environment is Cygwin, not native Win32. Install CMake,
Ninja or make, GCC, PCRE, and the desired optional dependency packages using
the Cygwin setup program.

From a Cygwin shell, follow the build instructions in ../README. CMake
automatically selects hardcoded ANSI terminal codes when no termcap-compatible
library is available.
